    - GCS immutability (#4134) by Mike McKay-Dirden
    - info about the B2 S3-compatible endpoint (#3860) by Wyatt
      Childers
    - upgraded rclone to 1.68.2, fixed Google Drive rclone
      compatibility (#4249) by Jarek Kowalski
